description:
The Smooth Jazz Cruise 2013 Week 1 : SmoothJazz.com's President Sandy Shore sits down with music host David Sanborn to discuss the uniqueness of The Smooth Jazz Cruise, his position on "Smooth Jazz", the history of the radio format and music business and more.
